{"tid":810643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"椅背裝針孔攝錄機　Uber司機涉偷拍女乘客春光被捕","createTime":"2018-09-08T06:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T07:57:23.000Z","uid":80516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eba88e78a78445986100a82f921a1f921102a6b4","tid":810643,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"新界南總區交通執行及管制組特遣隊警員，今日(8日)凌晨在區內多處地點進行打擊酒後駕駛行動‬，其中一名44歲姓黃司機在現場接受「吹波波」呼氣測試不合格，惟帶返警署以大機作呼氣測試時，錄得結果不超出法定標準。經警方調查後，相信涉案七人車用作非法出租載客取酬，當時車上有一名女乘客。<br />\n<br />\n警員搜查有關七人車發現有兩部針孔攝錄機，分別安裝於司機椅背及左前乘客椅背，懷疑用作偷拍後座乘客大腿位置。警員亦在該車輛內兩部智能電話發現多條不雅短片。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，黃為Uber司機，涉嫌「不誠實使用電腦」、「非法駕駛汽車作出租或載客取酬用途」及「駕駛汽車時沒有第三者保險」被捕，由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n是次行動中，警方共向288名司機進行酒精呼氣測試，其中3名年齡介乎23至66歲的男司機未能通過酒精呼氣測試，涉嫌「酒後駕駛」被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180908130852http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180908130852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180908130852http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180908130852&h=23e6be43&s={SIZE}\" />其中一偷拍鏡頭安裝於椅背上。(警方圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180908130852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180908130852&h=167078fa&s={SIZE}\" />涉案七人車被扣查。(警方圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180908130852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180908130852&h=97551ddd&s={SIZE}\" />檢獲的針孔攝錄機及電池。(警方圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_04p.jpg?20180908130852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20180908130852&h=a64d2aaa&s={SIZE}\" />車內放有多部手機。(警方圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_05p.jpg?20180908130852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20180908130852&h=27684f8d&s={SIZE}\" />椅背安裝有針孔攝錄機。(警方圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fbkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001.html&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4e88ae3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/bkn-20180908092627917-0908_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"99426130cb9bffa34b31a413df4e784174f78554","tid":810643,"uid":46682,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:56:08.000Z","msg":"都幾明顯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2595d8e9913e633512a768092f477b9d9adc75e5","tid":810643,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"又不誠實使用電腦？"},{"pid":"50b19f2cfa7fcdcd7275f925f5508ad133145691","tid":810643,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"偷拍個d係咪腦裝屎？<br />\n網上大把三四仔，睇十世都睇唔完，<br />\n要自己拍咁on 99?"},{"pid":"17ac0586ece6672573f92b2e7d8ade264eb14396","tid":810643,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99426130cb9bffa34b31a413df4e7